recentTweets.text:
Withdrawing from 66 international organizations is not America first. It is America alone.
 
@POTUS and @SecRubio should be working within organizations to shape and bring about positive outcomes for the American people. This move does the opposite. 
https://t.co/t9tjP5Xsy6

Denmark is an ally and friend of America. The people of Greenland are as well.

Rather than working to address the challenges facing Americans, President Trump is attacking our allies and undermining our relationships.

@HouseForeign RM Meeks and I demand answers.

